Release Notes for X-CUBE-MEMS1 Projects

Copyright © 2022 STMicroelectronics

Purpose

The X-CUBE-MEMS1 Projects provide examples and applications to aid understanding how to develop an application using the middlewares and drivers for the MEMS devices. Most projects include STM32CubeMX project file (.ioc) for the graphical visualization of the STM32 microcontroller pins, peripherals and middlewares configuration.

Update History

Main Changes

Maintenance release

  • Regenerate source code with CubeMX MEMS pack v9.3.0
  • Add new sensor: ASM330LHHX
  • Replace NUCLEO-L476RG examples and applications by NUCLEO-U575ZI-Q ones

Development Toolchains and Compilers

  • IAR Embedded Workbench for ARM (EWARM) toolchain V9.20.1
  • RealView Microcontroller Development Kit (MDK-ARM) toolchain V5.32.0
  • STM32CubeIDE V1.9.0

Supported Devices and Boards

  • STM32F401RE, STM32L073RZ, STM32L152RE and STM32U575ZI-Q devices
  • NUCLEO-F401RE Board RevC
  • NUCLEO-L073RZ Board RevC
  • NUCLEO-L152RE Board RevC
  • NUCLEO-U575ZI-Q Board RevC
  • X-NUCLEO-IKS01A2
  • X-NUCLEO-IKS01A3
  • X-NUCLEO-IKS02A1

Main Changes

Maintenance release

  • Regenerated the source code with CubeMX MEMS pack v9.2.0
  • Added new sensors: LIS2DU12, ILPS22QS, ILPS28QSW, LPS28DFW

Development Toolchains and Compilers

  • IAR Embedded Workbench for ARM (EWARM) toolchain V8.50.9
  • RealView Microcontroller Development Kit (MDK-ARM) toolchain V5.32.0
  • STM32CubeIDE V1.8.0

Supported Devices and Boards

  • STM32F401RE, STM32L073RZ, STM32L152RE and STM32L476RG devices
  • NUCLEO-F401RE Board RevC
  • NUCLEO-L073RZ Board RevC
  • NUCLEO-L152RE Board RevC
  • NUCLEO-L476RG Board RevC
  • X-NUCLEO-IKS01A2
  • X-NUCLEO-IKS01A3
  • X-NUCLEO-IKS02A1

Main Changes

Maintenance release

  • Regenerate the source code with CubeMX MEMS pack v9.1.0
  • Add new sensors: LIS2DTW12, LPS22DF
  • Add support for MKI217V1 (LSM6DSOX+LIS2MDL SensorHub DIL24) into IKS01A3 DataLogExtended example (special case)

The components flagged by “” have changed since the previous release. “” are new.

Development Toolchains and Compilers

  • IAR Embedded Workbench for ARM (EWARM) toolchain V8.50.9
  • RealView Microcontroller Development Kit (MDK-ARM) toolchain V5.32.0
  • STM32CubeIDE V1.7.0

Supported Devices and Boards

  • STM32F401RE, STM32L073RZ, STM32L152RE and STM32L476RG devices
  • NUCLEO-F401RE Board RevC
  • NUCLEO-L073RZ Board RevC
  • NUCLEO-L152RE Board RevC
  • NUCLEO-L476RG Board RevC
  • X-NUCLEO-IKS01A2
  • X-NUCLEO-IKS01A3
  • X-NUCLEO-IKS02A1

Main Changes

Product update

  • Regenerate the source code with CubeMX MEMS pack v9.0.0
  • Add new sensors: AIS2IH, LSM6DSO32X
  • Add support to Example Selector

The components flagged by “” have changed since the previous release. “” are new.

Development Toolchains and Compilers

  • IAR Embedded Workbench for ARM (EWARM) toolchain V8.50.9
  • RealView Microcontroller Development Kit (MDK-ARM) toolchain V5.32.0
  • STM32CubeIDE V1.6.1

Supported Devices and Boards

  • STM32F401RE, STM32L073RZ, STM32L152RE and STM32L476RG devices
  • NUCLEO-F401RE Board RevC
  • NUCLEO-L073RZ Board RevC
  • NUCLEO-L152RE Board RevC
  • NUCLEO-L476RG Board RevC
  • X-NUCLEO-IKS01A2
  • X-NUCLEO-IKS01A3
  • X-NUCLEO-IKS02A1

Maintenance release

  • Regenerate the source code with CubeMX MEMS pack v8.3.0
  • Update libraries

Development Toolchains and Compilers

  • IAR Embedded Workbench for ARM (EWARM) toolchain V8.50.5
  • RealView Microcontroller Development Kit (MDK-ARM) toolchain V5.29.0
  • STM32CubeIDE V1.5.0

Supported Devices and Boards

  • STM32F401RE, STM32L073RZ, STM32L152RE and STM32L476RG devices
  • NUCLEO-F401RE Board RevC
  • NUCLEO-L073RZ Board RevC
  • NUCLEO-L152RE Board RevC
  • NUCLEO-L476RG Board RevC
  • X-NUCLEO-IKS01A2
  • X-NUCLEO-IKS01A3
  • X-NUCLEO-IKS02A1

Development Toolchains and Compilers

  • IAR Embedded Workbench for ARM (EWARM) toolchain V8.32.3
  • RealView Microcontroller Development Kit (MDK-ARM) toolchain V5.29.0
  • STM32CubeIDE V1.3.0

Supported Devices and Boards

  • STM32F401RE, STM32L073RZ, STM32L152RE and STM32L476RG devices
  • NUCLEO-F401RE Board RevC
  • NUCLEO-L073RZ Board RevC
  • NUCLEO-L152RE Board RevC
  • NUCLEO-L476RG Board RevC
  • X-NUCLEO-IKS01A2
  • X-NUCLEO-IKS01A3
  • X-NUCLEO-IKS02A1

Patch release

  • Replace AccelCalibration2_IIS2ICLX, TiltSensing2_IIS2ICLX Middleware applications absolute by relative paths

  • IAR Embedded Workbench for ARM (EWARM) toolchain V8.32.3
  • RealView Microcontroller Development Kit (MDK-ARM) toolchain V5.29.0
  • STM32CubeIDE V1.3.0

Supported Devices and Boards

  • STM32F401RE, STM32L073RZ, STM32L152RE and STM32L476RG devices
  • NUCLEO-F401RE Board RevC

  • NUCLEO-L152RE Board RevC
  • NUCLEO-L476RG Board RevC

  • IAR Embedded Workbench for ARM (EWARM) toolchain V8.32.3
  • RealView Microcontroller Development Kit (MDK-ARM) toolchain V5.29.0
  • STM32CubeIDE V1.3.0

Supported Devices and Boards

  • STM32F401RE, STM32L073RZ, STM32L152RE and STM32L476RG devices
  • NUCLEO-F401RE Board RevC
  • NUCLEO-L073RZ Board RevC
  • NUCLEO-L152RE Board RevC
  • NUCLEO-L476RG Board RevC
  • X-NUCLEO-IKS01A2
  • X-NUCLEO-IKS01A3
  • X-NUCLEO-IKS02A1

  • STM32F401RE, STM32L073RZ, STM32L152RE and STM32L476RG devices
  • NUCLEO-F401RE Board RevC
  • NUCLEO-L073RZ Board RevC

  • NUCLEO-L476RG Board RevC
  • X-NUCLEO-IKS01A2
  • X-NUCLEO-IKS01A3
  • X-NUCLEO-IKS02A1

  • X-NUCLEO-IKS01A3
  • X-NUCLEO-IKS02A1

Main Changes

Maintenance release

  • Modifications in AccelerometerCalibration / CarryPosition / DataLogFusion / ECompass / GestureRecognition / GyroscopeCalibration / IntensityDetection / MagnetometerCalibration / TiltSensing / VerticalContext
  • Regenerate the source code with CubeMX MEMS pack v7.1.0
  • Remove support of flash memory for offline data storage
  • Add Cortex-M7 support
  • Add library elapsed time measurement feature

  • IAR Embedded Workbench for ARM (EWARM) toolchain V8.32.3
  • RealView Microcontroller Development Kit (MDK-ARM) toolchain V5.27.1
  • STM32CubeIDE V1.2.0

  • STM32F401RE, STM32L073RZ, STM32L152RE and STM32L476RG devices
  • NUCLEO-F401RE Board RevC

Main Changes

Product update

  • Update examples and applications to be compatible with CubeMX v5.4.0
  • Add support to X-NUCLEO-IKS02A1
  • Add support for DIL24 sensors into BSP layer and DataLogExtended example

Development Toolchains and Compilers

  • IAR Embedded Workbench for ARM (EWARM) toolchain V8.32.3
  • RealView Microcontroller Development Kit (MDK-ARM) toolchain V5.27.1
  • System Workbench for STM32 V2.9.1.20190503

Supported Devices and Boards

  • STM32F401RE, STM32L073RZ, STM32L152RE and STM32L476RG devices
  • NUCLEO-F401RE Board RevC
  • NUCLEO-L073RZ Board RevC
  • NUCLEO-L152RE Board RevC
  • NUCLEO-L476RG Board RevC
  • X-NUCLEO-IKS01A2
  • X-NUCLEO-IKS01A3
  • X-NUCLEO-IKS02A1

Main Changes

Maintenance release

  • Update examples and applications to be compatible with CubeMX v5.2.1
  • Add library and application for Vibration Monitoring algorithm
  • Add support for DIL24 sensors into BSP layer and DataLogExtended example
  • Convert IAR projects from v7 to v8 and switch libraries from wchar16 to wchar32

Contents

The components flagged by “” have changed since the previous release. “” are new.

Development Toolchains and Compilers

  • IAR Embedded Workbench for ARM (EWARM) toolchain V8.20.2
  • RealView Microcontroller Development Kit (MDK-ARM) toolchain V5.24.2
  • System Workbench for STM32 V2.8.1.20190305

Supported Devices and Boards

  • STM32F401RE, STM32L073RZ, STM32L152RE and STM32L476RG devices
  • NUCLEO-F401RE Board RevC
  • NUCLEO-L073RZ Board RevC
  • NUCLEO-L152RE Board RevC
  • NUCLEO-L476RG Board RevC
  • X-NUCLEO-IKS01A2
  • X-NUCLEO-IKS01A3

  • Add auto-discovery of components attached via DIL24 interface
  • Add multi-platform support for project examples
  • Add support for LPS25HB sensor via DIL24 interface

Development Toolchains and Compilers

  • IAR Embedded Workbench for ARM (EWARM) toolchain V7.30
  • RealView Microcontroller Development Kit (MDK-ARM) toolchain V5.12
  • Atollic TrueSTUDIO for ARM Pro V5.2.1

Supported Devices and Boards

  • STM32F401RE and STM32L053R8 devices
  • NUCLEO-F401RE Board RevC
  • NUCLEO-L053R8 Board RevC
  • X-NUCLEO-IKS01A1
